### 프로필 등록 (회원가입)
POST {{baseUrl}}/profile/create
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "홍길동",
  "bio": "안녕하세요",
  "profileImageUrl": "https://example.com/image.jpg",
  "emotionTagIds": [1, 2]
}

### 내 프로필 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/profile/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 프로필 수정 (닉네임만 변경)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/profile/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "새닉네임"
}

### 프로필 수정 (감정 태그 변경)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/profile/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "emotionTagIds": [1, 3, 5]
}

### 프로필 수정 (전체 변경)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/profile/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "새닉네임",
  "bio": "새 소개글",
  "profileImageUrl": "https://example.com/new.jpg",
  "emotionTagIds": [2, 4]
}
